author: Grant Segall, The Plain Dealer
title: Kelly Flamos and Colin McEwen offer bowling, bands and more at Mahall's in Lakewood: My Cleveland (photos)
text: Kelly Flamos and Colin McEwen are partners in marriage and at Mahall's 20 Lanes of Lakewood, believed to be Ohio's oldest surviving bowling alley at age 93.
